Article 9 (Formulation of Comprehensive Plans for Promotion of Nuclear Energy)
* The Minister of Science, Information and Communications Technology (ICT) and Future Planning
* Each comprehensive plan shall include the following matters:
* Current state of and prospects for the use of nuclear energy;
* Policy objectives of and basic direction-setting for the use of nuclear energy;
* Sectoral tasks and the promotion thereof;
* Investment plans and financing of required financial resources;
* Other matters necessary for the use of nuclear energy.
